txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Large wings from birds near Trestlebridge. Deliver the items to Guardsman Otley in the town of Trestlebridge.
'We can find uses for these. Thank you.'
'We could use new bedding for people here in town. If you can get some wings for us, we'll take care of stuffing the beds.'
Men of Bree Task: Large Wings
Guardsman Otley, in Trestlebridge, is awaiting delivery of large wings.
Deliver the large wings to Guardsman Otley at Trestlebridge
You have been tasked with collecting large wings from birds near Trestlebridge.\n\nYou can deliver the items to Guardsman Otley at Trestlebridge.
Wanted: Large wings from birds near Trestlebridge.
